嚇到朋友面都青埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf68233c4dad12b2048645c4bb3f73fc089841d5","tid":1184604,"uid":189859,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:30:12.000Z","msg":"每次同朋友打邊爐叫辣 <br />\n每次都話食唔到辣<br />\n我都會西一西面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571aa2e172fb040fcc6fade409f3b79c5a4cd015","tid":1184604,"uid":20006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:31:53.000Z","msg":"以前食唔到辣<br />\n依家練到可以食譚仔中辣, 遲下挑戰大辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b350caba000b97461cc70c7e1d7106a699af94","tid":1184604,"uid":85232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T00:35:21.000Z","msg":"食咁辣，小心啲腸胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}